"title": "7203: ark, Noah's",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7203",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The craft built at God's command by Noah and his family as a means of escape from the flood. The ark is seen as corresponding to the redemption offered to believers through Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>The building of the ark</h2>\n<h3>The command to build</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:14\">GEN 6:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:1-Gen6:13\">GEN 6:1–6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:15-Gen6:16\">GEN 6:15–6:16</a></p>\n<h3>Its purpose for Noah and his family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:17-Gen6:18\">GEN 6:17–6:18</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Its purpose for the animals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:19\">GEN 6:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:20-Gen6:22\">GEN 6:20–6:22</a></p>\n<h2>The ark and the flood</h2>\n<h3>Noah obeyed God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:5\">GEN 7:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:1-Gen7:4\">GEN 7:1–7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:6-Gen7:16\">GEN 7:6–7:16</a></p>\n<h3>The ark served its purpose</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:17\">GEN 7:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:18-Gen7:24\">GEN 7:18–7:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:1-Gen8:19\">GEN 8:1–8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:1-Gen9:17\">GEN 9:1–9:17</a></p>\n<h2>The significance of the ark elsewhere in Scripture</h2>\n<h3>An instance of judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:38-Matt24:39\">MAT 24:38–24:39</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:26-Luke17:27\">LUK 17:26–17:27</a> <em>Judgment clearly divides humanity into the saved and the lost.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:5\">2PE 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>An example of faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:7\">HEB 11:7</a></strong> <em>Noah took God at his word in circumstances which must have appeared ridiculous.</em></p>\n<h3>A symbol of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:20-1Pet3:21\">1PE 3:20–3:21</a></strong> <em>The link between the ark and baptism is in the twin ideas of water and salvation.</em></p>",
